name: bulbasaur
flavor_text_entries: A strange seed was planted on its back at birth. The plant sprouts and grows with this POKéMON.

name: ivysaur
flavor_text_entries: When the bulb on its back grows large, it appears to lose the ability to stand on its hind legs.

name: venusaur
flavor_text_entries: The plant blooms when it is absorbing solar energy. It stays on the move to seek sunlight.

name: charmander
flavor_text_entries: Obviously prefers hot places. When it rains, steam is said to spout from the tip of its tail.

name: charmeleon
flavor_text_entries: When it swings its burning tail, it elevates the temperature to unbearably high levels.

name: charizard
flavor_text_entries: Spits fire that is hot enough to melt boulders. Known to cause forest fires unintentionally.

name: squirtle
flavor_text_entries: Shoots water at prey while in the water. Withdraws into its shell when in danger.

name: wartortle
flavor_text_entries: When tapped, this POKéMON will pull in its head, but its tail will still stick out a little bit.

name: blastoise
flavor_text_entries: It deliberately makes itself heavy so it can with­ stand the recoil of the water jets it fires.

name: caterpie
flavor_text_entries: It releases a stench from its red antenna to repel enemies. It grows by molting repeatedly.

name: metapod
flavor_text_entries: This POKéMON is vulnerable to attack while its shell is soft, exposing its weak and tender body.

name: butterfree
flavor_text_entries: In battle, it flaps its wings at high speed to release highly toxic dust into the air.

name: weedle
flavor_text_entries: Often found in forests, eating leaves. It has a sharp venomous stinger on its head.

name: kakuna
flavor_text_entries: Almost incapable of moving, this POKéMON can only harden its shell to protect itself from predators.

name: beedrill
flavor_text_entries: Flies at high speed and attacks using its large venomous stingers on its forelegs and tail.

name: pidgey
flavor_text_entries: A common sight in forests and woods. It flaps its wings at ground level to kick up blinding sand.

name: pidgeotto
flavor_text_entries: Very protective of its sprawling territorial area, this POKéMON will fiercely peck at any intruder.

name: pidgeot
flavor_text_entries: When hunting, it skims the surface of water at high speed to pick off unwary prey such as MAGIKARP.

name: rattata
flavor_text_entries: Bites anything when it attacks. Small and very quick, it is a common sight in many places.

name: raticate
flavor_text_entries: It uses its whis­ kers to maintain its balance. It apparently slows down if they are cut off.

name: spearow
flavor_text_entries: Il est incapable de voler à haute altitude. Il se déplace très vite pour protéger son territoire.

name: fearow
flavor_text_entries: With its huge and magnificent wings, it can keep aloft without ever having to land for rest.

name: ekans
flavor_text_entries: Moves silently and stealthily. Eats the eggs of birds, such as PIDGEY and SPEAROW, whole.

name: arbok
flavor_text_entries: It is rumored that the ferocious warning markings on its belly differ from area to area.

name: pikachu
flavor_text_entries: 最近發表了聚集大量皮卡丘 來建造發電廠的計畫。

name: raichu
flavor_text_entries: Its tail discharges electricity into the ground, protecting it from getting shocked.

name: sandshrew
flavor_text_entries: Burrows deep underground in arid locations far from water. It only emerges to hunt for food.

name: sandslash
flavor_text_entries: Curls up into a spiny ball when threatened. It can roll while curled up to attack or escape.

name: nidoran-f
flavor_text_entries: Although small, its venomous barbs render this POKéMON dangerous. The female has smaller horns.

name: nidorina
flavor_text_entries: The female's horn develops slowly. Prefers physical attacks such as clawing and biting.

name: nidoqueen
flavor_text_entries: Its hard scales provide strong protection. It uses its hefty bulk to execute powerful moves.

name: nidoran-m
flavor_text_entries: Saca las orejas por encima de la hierba para explorar el territorio. Le protege su cuerno venenoso.

name: nidorino
flavor_text_entries: An aggressive POKéMON that is quick to attack. The horn on its head secretes a powerful venom.

name: nidoking
flavor_text_entries: One swing of its mighty tail can snap a telephone pole as if it were a matchstick.

name: clefairy
flavor_text_entries: Its magical and cute appeal has many admirers. It is rare and found only in certain areas.

name: clefable
flavor_text_entries: A timid fairy POKéMON that is rarely seen. It will run and hide the moment it senses people.

name: vulpix
flavor_text_entries: At the time of birth, it has just one tail. The tail splits from its tip as it grows older.

name: ninetales
flavor_text_entries: Very smart and very vengeful. Grabbing one of its many tails could result in a 1000-year curse.

name: jigglypuff
flavor_text_entries: When its huge eyes light up, it sings a mysteriously soothing melody that lulls its enemies to sleep.

name: wigglytuff
flavor_text_entries: The body is soft and rubbery. When angered, it will suck in air and inflate itself to an enormous size.

name: zubat
flavor_text_entries: Forms colonies in perpetually dark places. Uses ultrasonic waves to identify and approach targets.

name: golbat
flavor_text_entries: Once it strikes, it will not stop draining energy from the victim even if it gets too heavy to fly.

name: oddish
flavor_text_entries: During the day, it keeps its face buried in the ground. At night, it wanders around sowing its seeds.

name: gloom
flavor_text_entries: It secretes a sticky, drool-like honey. Although sweet, it smells too repulsive to get very close.

name: vileplume
flavor_text_entries: It has the world's largest petals. With every step, the petals shake out heavy clouds of toxic pollen.

name: paras
flavor_text_entries: Burrows to suck tree roots. The mushrooms on its back grow by draw­ ing nutrients from the bug host.

name: parasect
flavor_text_entries: A host-parasite pair in which the parasite mushroom has taken over the host bug. Prefers damp places.

name: venonat
flavor_text_entries: Lives in the shadows of tall trees where it eats insects. It is attracted by light at night.

name: venomoth
flavor_text_entries: The dust-like scales covering its wings are color coded to indicate the kinds of poison it has.

name: diglett
flavor_text_entries: Lives about one yard underground where it feeds on plant roots. It sometimes appears above ground.

name: dugtrio
flavor_text_entries: A team of DIGLETT triplets. It triggers huge earthquakes by burrowing 60 miles underground.

name: meowth
flavor_text_entries: Es de naturaleza nocturna. Le atraen los objetos brillantes.

name: persian
flavor_text_entries: Although its fur has many admirers, it is tough to raise as a pet because of its fickle meanness.

name: psyduck
flavor_text_entries: While lulling its enemies with its vacant look, this wily POKéMON will use psychokinetic powers.

name: golduck
flavor_text_entries: Often seen swim­ ming elegantly by lake shores. It is often mistaken for the Japanese monster, Kappa.

name: mankey
flavor_text_entries: Extremely quick to anger. It could be docile one moment then thrashing away the next instant.

name: primeape
flavor_text_entries: Always furious and tenacious to boot. It will not abandon chasing its quarry until it is caught.

name: growlithe
flavor_text_entries: Very protective of its territory. It will bark and bite to repel intruders from its space.

name: arcanine
flavor_text_entries: A POKéMON that has been admired since the past for its beauty. It runs agilely as if on wings.

name: poliwag
flavor_text_entries: Its newly grown legs prevent it from running. It appears to prefer swimming than trying to stand.

name: poliwhirl
flavor_text_entries: Capable of living in or out of water. When out of water, it sweats to keep its body slimy.

name: poliwrath
flavor_text_entries: An adept swimmer at both the front crawl and breast stroke. Easily overtakes the best human swimmers.

name: abra
flavor_text_entries: Dieses Pokémon schläft 18 Stunden am Tag. Bei Gefahr teleportiert es sich in Sicherheit, ohne dabei aufzuwachen.

name: kadabra
flavor_text_entries: It emits special alpha waves from its body that induce headaches just by being close by.

name: alakazam
flavor_text_entries: Its brain can out­ perform a super­ computer. Its intelligence quotient is said to be 5,000.

name: machop
flavor_text_entries: Loves to build its muscles. It trains in all styles of martial arts to become even stronger.

name: machoke
flavor_text_entries: Its muscular body is so powerful, it must wear a power save belt to be able to regulate its motions.

name: machamp
flavor_text_entries: Using its heavy muscles, it throws powerful punches that can send the victim clear over the horizon.

name: bellsprout
flavor_text_entries: Even though its body is extremely skinny, it is blindingly fast when catching its prey.

name: weepinbell
flavor_text_entries: Escupe Polvo Veneno para envenenar al enemigo y, luego, lo liquida con Ácido.

name: victreebel
flavor_text_entries: Said to live in huge colonies deep in jungles, although no one has ever returned from there.

name: tentacool
flavor_text_entries: Son corps est principalement composé d’eau. Ses yeux cristallins projettent d’étranges rayons.

name: tentacruel
flavor_text_entries: 80개의 촉수를 자유롭게 움직인다. 찔리면 독이 퍼져 극심한 고통을 겪게 된다.

name: geodude
flavor_text_entries: Found in fields and mountains. Mistaking them for boulders, people often step or trip on them.

name: graveler
flavor_text_entries: Rolls down slopes to move. It rolls over any obstacle without slowing or changing its direction.

name: golem
flavor_text_entries: Its boulder-like body is extremely hard. It can easily withstand dynamite blasts without damage.

name: ponyta
flavor_text_entries: Its hooves are 10 times harder than diamonds. It can trample anything completely flat in little time.

name: rapidash
flavor_text_entries: Very competitive, this POKéMON will chase anything that moves fast in the hopes of racing it.

name: slowpoke
flavor_text_entries: Incredibly slow and dopey. It takes 5 seconds for it to feel pain when under attack.

name: slowbro
flavor_text_entries: The SHELLDER that is latched onto SLOWPOKE's tail is said to feed on the host's left over scraps.

name: magnemite
flavor_text_entries: Uses anti-gravity to stay suspended. Appears without warning and uses THUNDER WAVE and similar moves.

name: magneton
flavor_text_entries: Formed by several MAGNEMITEs linked together. They frequently appear when sunspots flare up.

name: farfetchd
flavor_text_entries: The sprig of green onions it holds is its weapon. It is used much like a metal sword.

name: doduo
flavor_text_entries: A bird that makes up for its poor flying with its fast foot speed. Leaves giant footprints.

name: dodrio
flavor_text_entries: Uses its three brains to execute complex plans. While two heads sleep, one head stays awake.

name: seel
flavor_text_entries: The protruding horn on its head is very hard. It is used for bashing through thick ice.

name: dewgong
flavor_text_entries: Stores thermal energy in its body. Swims at a steady 8 knots even in intensely cold waters.

name: grimer
flavor_text_entries: Appears in filthy areas. Thrives by sucking up polluted sludge that is pumped out of factories.

name: muk
flavor_text_entries: Thickly covered with a filthy, vile sludge. It is so toxic, even its footprints contain poison.

name: shellder
flavor_text_entries: Its hard shell repels any kind of attack. It is vulnerable only when its shell is open.

name: cloyster
flavor_text_entries: CLOYSTER that live in seas with harsh tidal currents grow large, sharp spikes on their shells.

name: gastly
flavor_text_entries: Almost invisible, this gaseous POKéMON cloaks the target and puts it to sleep without notice.

name: haunter
flavor_text_entries: Because of its ability to slip through block walls, it is said to be from an­ other dimension.

name: gengar
flavor_text_entries: Under a full moon, this POKéMON likes to mimic the shadows of people and laugh at their fright.

name: onix
flavor_text_entries: As it grows, the stone portions of its body harden to become similar to a diamond, but colored black.

name: drowzee
flavor_text_entries: Puts enemies to sleep then eats their dreams. Occasionally gets sick from eating bad dreams.

name: hypno
flavor_text_entries: When it locks eyes with an enemy, it will use a mix of PSI moves such as HYPNOSIS and CONFUSION.

name: krabby
flavor_text_entries: Its pincers are not only powerful weapons, they are used for balance when walking sideways.

name: kingler
flavor_text_entries: The large pincer has 10000 hp of crushing power. However, its huge size makes it unwieldy to use.

name: voltorb
flavor_text_entries: Usually found in power plants. Easily mistaken for a POKé BALL, they have zapped many people.

name: electrode
flavor_text_entries: It stores electric energy under very high pressure. It often explodes with little or no provocation.

name: exeggcute
flavor_text_entries: Often mistaken for eggs. When disturbed, they quickly gather and attack in swarms.

name: exeggutor
flavor_text_entries: Legend has it that on rare occasions, one of its heads will drop off and continue on as an EXEGGCUTE.

name: cubone
flavor_text_entries: 死に別れた　母親の　骨を 頭に　覆っている。寂しいとき 大声で　泣くという。

name: marowak
flavor_text_entries: 骨に　灯った　呪いの　炎は いつまでも　治らない　痛みを 体と　心に　残すという。

name: hitmonlee
flavor_text_entries: When in a hurry, its legs lengthen progressively. It runs smoothly with extra long, loping strides.

name: hitmonchan
flavor_text_entries: While apparently doing nothing, it fires punches in lightning fast volleys that are impossible to see.

name: lickitung
flavor_text_entries: Its tongue can be extended like a chameleon's. It leaves a tingling sensation when it licks enemies.

name: koffing
flavor_text_entries: Because it stores several kinds of toxic gases in its body, it is prone to exploding without warning.

name: weezing
flavor_text_entries: Where two kinds of poison gases meet, 2 KOFFINGs can fuse into a WEEZING over many years.

name: rhyhorn
flavor_text_entries: Its massive bones are 1000 times harder than human bones. It can easily knock a trailer flying.

name: rhydon
flavor_text_entries: Protected by an armor-like hide, it is capable of living in molten lava of 3,600 degrees.

name: chansey
flavor_text_entries: A rare and elusive POKéMON that is said to bring happiness to those who manage to get it.

name: tangela
flavor_text_entries: The whole body is swathed with wide vines that are similar to sea­ weed. Its vines shake as it walks.

name: kangaskhan
flavor_text_entries: The infant rarely ventures out of its mother's protective pouch until it is 3 years old.

name: horsea
flavor_text_entries: Hace su nido entre los corales. Si se siente en peligro, escupe tinta y huye.

name: seadra
flavor_text_entries: Capable of swim­ ming backwards by rapidly flapping its wing-like pectoral fins and stout tail.

name: goldeen
flavor_text_entries: せびれ　むなびれ　おびれが ゆうがに　たなびくので みずのおどりこ　とよばれる。

name: seaking
flavor_text_entries: In the autumn spawning season, they can be seen swimming power­ fully up rivers and creeks.

name: staryu
flavor_text_entries: An enigmatic POKéMON that can effortlessly regenerate any appendage it loses in battle.

name: starmie
flavor_text_entries: Its central core glows with the seven colors of the rainbow. Some people value the core as a gem.

name: mr-mime
flavor_text_entries: If interrupted while it is miming, it will slap around the offender with its broad hands.

name: scyther
flavor_text_entries: With ninja-like agility and speed, it can create the illusion that there is more than one.

name: jynx
flavor_text_entries: Its cries sound like human speech. However, it is impossible to tell what it is trying to say.

name: electabuzz
flavor_text_entries: Normally found near power plants, they can wander away and cause major blackouts in cities.

name: magmar
flavor_text_entries: Its body always burns with an orange glow that enables it to hide perfectly among flames.

name: pinsir
flavor_text_entries: If it fails to crush the victim in its pincers, it will swing it around and toss it hard.

name: tauros
flavor_text_entries: When it targets an enemy, it charges furiously while whipping its body with its long tails.

name: magikarp
flavor_text_entries: In the distant past, it was somewhat stronger than the horribly weak descendants that exist today.

name: gyarados
flavor_text_entries: Rarely seen in the wild. Huge and vicious, it is capable of destroying entire cities in a rage.

name: lapras
flavor_text_entries: A POKéMON that has been over­ hunted almost to extinction. It can ferry people across the water.

name: ditto
flavor_text_entries: It can freely recombine its own cellular structure to transform into other life-forms.

name: eevee
flavor_text_entries: Its genetic code is irregular. It may mutate if it is exposed to radiation from element STONEs.

name: vaporeon
flavor_text_entries: 수중에서의 생활에 적합한 몸으로 진화했다. 물에 녹으면 보이지 않게 된다.

name: jolteon
flavor_text_entries: It accumulates negative ions in the atmosphere to blast out 10000- volt lightning bolts.

name: flareon
flavor_text_entries: When storing thermal energy in its body, its temperature could soar to over 1600 degrees.

name: porygon
flavor_text_entries: A POKéMON that consists entirely of programming code. Capable of moving freely in cyberspace.

name: omanyte
flavor_text_entries: Although long extinct, in rare cases, it can be genetically resurrected from fossils.

name: omastar
flavor_text_entries: Apparently, it cracked SHELLDER's shell with its sharp fangs and sucked out the insides.

name: kabuto
flavor_text_entries: A POKéMON that was resurrected from a fossil found in what was once the ocean floor eons ago.

name: kabutops
flavor_text_entries: Its sleek shape is perfect for swim­ ming. It slashes prey with its claws and drains the body fluids.

name: aerodactyl
flavor_text_entries: A ferocious, pre­ historic POKéMON that goes for the enemy's throat with its serrated saw-like fangs.

name: snorlax
flavor_text_entries: Very lazy. Just eats and sleeps. As its rotund bulk builds, it becomes steadily more slothful.

name: articuno
flavor_text_entries: A legendary bird POKéMON that is said to appear to doomed people who are lost in icy mountains.

name: zapdos
flavor_text_entries: A legendary bird POKéMON that is said to appear from clouds while dropping enormous lightning bolts.

name: moltres
flavor_text_entries: It is said to be the legendary bird Pokémon of fire. Every flap of its wings creates a dazzling flare of flames.

name: dratini
flavor_text_entries: Long considered a mythical POKéMON until recently when a small colony was found living underwater.

name: dragonair
flavor_text_entries: A mystical POKéMON that exudes a gentle aura. Has the ability to change climate conditions.

name: dragonite
flavor_text_entries: An extremely rarely seen marine POKéMON. Its intelligence is said to match that of humans.

name: mewtwo
flavor_text_entries: It was created by a scientist after years of horrific gene splicing and DNA engineering experiments.

name: mew
flavor_text_entries: So rare that it is still said to be a mirage by many experts. Only a few people have seen it worldwide.

name: chikorita
flavor_text_entries: A sweet aroma gently wafts from the leaf on its head. It is docile and loves to soak up the sun's rays.

name: bayleef
flavor_text_entries: Die Knospen an seinem Hals geben ein würziges Aroma ab, das andere aufheitert.

name: meganium
flavor_text_entries: The aroma that rises from its petals contains a substance that calms aggressive feelings.

name: cyndaquil
flavor_text_entries: It is timid, and always curls it­ self up in a ball. If attacked, it flares up its back for protection.

name: quilava
flavor_text_entries: Be careful if it turns its back during battle. It means that it will attack with the fire on its back.

name: typhlosion
flavor_text_entries: If its rage peaks, it becomes so hot that anything that touches it will instantly go up in flames.

name: totodile
flavor_text_entries: Its well-developed jaws are powerful and capable of crushing anything. Even its trainer must be careful.

name: croconaw
flavor_text_entries: If it loses a fang, a new one grows back in its place. There are always 48 fangs lining its mouth.

name: feraligatr
flavor_text_entries: When it bites with its massive and powerful jaws, it shakes its head and savagely tears its victim up.

name: sentret
flavor_text_entries: A very cautious POKéMON, it raises itself up using its tail to get a better view of its surroundings.

name: furret
flavor_text_entries: The mother puts its offspring to sleep by curling up around them. It corners foes with speed.

name: hoothoot
flavor_text_entries: It always stands on one foot. It changes feet so fast, the movement can rarely be seen.

name: noctowl
flavor_text_entries: Its eyes are specially adapted. They concentrate even faint light and enable it to see in the dark.

name: ledyba
flavor_text_entries: It is very timid. It will be afraid to move if it is alone. But it will be active if it is in a group.

name: ledian
flavor_text_entries: When the stars flicker in the night sky, it flutters about, scattering a glowing powder.

name: spinarak
flavor_text_entries: It lies still in the same pose for days in its web, waiting for its unsuspecting prey to wander close.

name: ariados
flavor_text_entries: It spins string not only from its rear but also from its mouth. It is hard to tell which end is which.

name: crobat
flavor_text_entries: It flies so si­ lently through the dark on its four wings that it may not be noticed even when nearby.

name: chinchou
flavor_text_entries: It shoots positive and negative elec­ tricity between the tips of its two antennae and zaps its enemies.

name: lanturn
flavor_text_entries: The light it emits is so bright that it can illuminate the sea's surface from a depth of over three miles.

name: pichu
flavor_text_entries: It is not yet skilled at storing electricity. It may send out a jolt if amused or startled.

name: cleffa
flavor_text_entries: Si dice che sia facile incontrarlo dove sono precipitate delle stelle cadenti.

name: igglybuff
flavor_text_entries: It has a very soft body. If it starts to roll, it will bounce all over and be impossible to stop.

name: togepi
flavor_text_entries: The shell seems to be filled with joy. It is said that it will share good luck when treated kindly.

name: togetic
flavor_text_entries: They say that it will appear before kindhearted, car­ ing people and shower them with happiness.

name: natu
flavor_text_entries: Because its wings aren't yet fully grown, it has to hop to get around. It is always star­ ing at something.

name: xatu
flavor_text_entries: They say that it stays still and quiet because it is seeing both the past and future at the same time.

name: mareep
flavor_text_entries: If static elec­ tricity builds in its body, its fleece doubles in volume. Touching it will shock you.

name: flaaffy
flavor_text_entries: As a result of storing too much electricity, it developed patches where even downy wool won't grow.

name: ampharos
flavor_text_entries: The tail's tip shines brightly and can be seen from far away. It acts as a beacon for lost people.

name: bellossom
flavor_text_entries: BELLOSSOM gather at times and appear to dance. They say that the dance is a ritual to summon the sun.

name: marill
flavor_text_entries: The tip of its tail, which con­ tains oil that is lighter than wa­ ter, lets it swim without drowning.

name: azumarill
flavor_text_entries: 会制作填满空气的泡泡。 当露力丽在河里玩的时候， 它就会用这个泡泡包住露力丽。

name: sudowoodo
flavor_text_entries: Although it always pretends to be a tree, its composi­ tion appears to be closer to a rock than a plant.

name: politoed
flavor_text_entries: 울음소리가 울려 퍼지면 여기저기에서 발챙이와 슈륙챙이들이 모인다.

name: hoppip
flavor_text_entries: To keep from being blown away by the wind, they gather in clusters. They do enjoy gentle breezes, though.

name: skiploom
flavor_text_entries: The bloom on top of its head opens and closes as the temperature fluc­ tuates up and down.

name: jumpluff
flavor_text_entries: Once it catches the wind, it deft­ ly controls its cotton-puff spores to float, even around the world.

name: aipom
flavor_text_entries: Its tail is so powerful that it can use it to grab a tree branch and hold itself up in the air.

name: sunkern
flavor_text_entries: It may drop out of the sky suddenly. If attacked by a SPEAROW, it will violently shake its leaves.

name: sunflora
flavor_text_entries: 태양 에너지에서 영양을 만들어낸다. 기온이 높은 낮에는 활발하게 움직이고 태양이 지면 뚝 하니 움직이지 않게 된다.

name: yanma
flavor_text_entries: If it flaps its wings really fast, it can generate shock waves that will shatter win­ dows in the area.

name: wooper
flavor_text_entries: This POKéMON lives in cold water. It will leave the water to search for food when it gets cold outside.

name: quagsire
flavor_text_entries: This carefree POKéMON has an easy-going nature. While swimming, it always bumps into boat hulls.

name: espeon
flavor_text_entries: It uses the fine hair that covers its body to sense air currents and predict its ene­ my's actions.

name: umbreon
flavor_text_entries: When agitated, this POKéMON pro­ tects itself by spraying poisonous sweat from its pores.

name: murkrow
flavor_text_entries: Feared and loathed by many, it is believed to bring misfortune to all those who see it at night.

name: slowking
flavor_text_entries: It has incredible intellect and in­ tuition. Whatever the situation, it remains calm and collected.

name: misdreavus
flavor_text_entries: It likes playing mischievous tricks such as screaming and wailing to startle people at night.

name: unown
flavor_text_entries: Its flat, thin body is always stuck on walls. Its shape appears to have some meaning.

name: wobbuffet
flavor_text_entries: It hates light and shock. If attack­ ed, it inflates its body to pump up its counter­ strike.

name: girafarig
flavor_text_entries: Its tail has a small brain of its own. Beware! If you get close, it may react to your scent and bite.

name: pineco
flavor_text_entries: It likes to make its shell thicker by adding layers of tree bark. The additional weight doesn't bother it.

name: forretress
flavor_text_entries: Its entire body is shielded by a steel-hard shell. What lurks inside the armor is a total mystery.

name: dunsparce
flavor_text_entries: DUNSPARCE has a drill for its tail. It uses this tail to burrow into the ground backwards. This POKéMON is known to make its nest in complex shapes deep under the ground.

name: gligar
flavor_text_entries: It flies straight at its target’s face, then clamps down on the startled victim to inject poison.

name: steelix
flavor_text_entries: Its body has been compressed deep under the ground. As a result, it is even harder than a diamond.

name: snubbull
flavor_text_entries: Although it looks frightening, it is actually kind and affectionate. It is very popular among women.

name: granbull
flavor_text_entries: It is actually timid and easily spooked. If at­ tacked, it flails about to fend off its attacker.

name: qwilfish
flavor_text_entries: To fire its poison spikes, it must inflate its body by drinking over 2.6 gallons of water all at once.

name: scizor
flavor_text_entries: It swings its eye- patterned pincers up to scare its foes. This makes it look like it has three heads.

name: shuckle
flavor_text_entries: The BERRIES it stores in its vase-like shell decompose and become a gooey liquid.

name: heracross
flavor_text_entries: This powerful POKéMON thrusts its prized horn under its enemies’ bellies then lifts and throws them.

name: sneasel
flavor_text_entries: Its paws conceal sharp claws. If attacked, it sud­ denly extends the claws and startles its enemy.

name: teddiursa
flavor_text_entries: If it finds honey, its crescent mark glows. It always licks its paws because they are soaked with honey.

name: ursaring
flavor_text_entries: Avec sa capacité à sentir toute odeur, il trouve sans faillir de la nourriture enfouie dans le sol.

name: slugma
flavor_text_entries: Son corps est fait de magma. S’il cesse de bouger, il refroidit et durcit.

name: magcargo
flavor_text_entries: The shell on its back is just skin that has cooled and hardened. It breaks easily with a slight touch.

name: swinub
flavor_text_entries: It rubs its snout on the ground to find and dig up food. It sometimes discovers hot springs.

name: piloswine
flavor_text_entries: Because the long hair all over its body obscures its sight, it just keeps charging repeatedly.

name: corsola
flavor_text_entries: It continuously sheds and grows. The tip of its head is prized as a treasure for its beauty.

name: remoraid
flavor_text_entries: It squirts water forcefully from its mouth to shoot down flying prey.

name: octillery
flavor_text_entries: It traps enemies with its suction- cupped tentacles then smashes them with its rock-hard head.

name: delibird
flavor_text_entries: It carries food all day long. There are tales about lost people who were saved by the food it had.

name: mantine
flavor_text_entries: As it majestically swims, it doesn't care if REMORAID attach to it for scavenging its leftovers.

name: skarmory
flavor_text_entries: 全身披著鋼鐵鎧甲。 看起來很重，但牠能以 最高３００公里的時速飛行。

name: houndour
flavor_text_entries: It uses different kinds of cries for communicating with others of its kind and for pursuing its prey.

name: houndoom
flavor_text_entries: If you are burned by the flames it shoots from its mouth, the pain will never go away.

name: kingdra
flavor_text_entries: Dicen que suele esconderse en cuevas submarinas. Puede crear torbellinos al bostezar.

name: phanpy
flavor_text_entries: It swings its long snout around play­ fully, but because it is so strong, that can be dan­ gerous.

name: donphan
flavor_text_entries: It has sharp, hard tusks and a rugged hide. Its TACKLE is strong enough to knock down a house.

name: porygon2
flavor_text_entries: This upgraded version of PORYGON is designed for space exploration. It can't fly, though.

name: stantler
flavor_text_entries: Those who stare at its antlers will gradually lose control of their senses and be unable to stand.

name: smeargle
flavor_text_entries: A special fluid oozes from the tip of its tail. It paints the fluid everywhere to mark its territory.

name: tyrogue
flavor_text_entries: It is always bursting with en­ ergy. To make it­ self stronger, it keeps on fighting even if it loses.

name: hitmontop
flavor_text_entries: Si te encantan sus suaves, elegantes y danzarinas patadas, acabarás taladrado.

name: smoochum
flavor_text_entries: Its lips are the most sensitive parts on its body. It always uses its lips first to examine things.

name: elekid
flavor_text_entries: It generates electricity by whirling its arms. However, it can’t store the energy it makes.

name: magby
flavor_text_entries: Each and every time it inhales and exhales, hot embers dribble out of its mouth and nostrils.

name: miltank
flavor_text_entries: Its milk is packed with nutrition, making it the ultimate beverage for the sick or weary.

name: blissey
flavor_text_entries: Anyone who takes even one bite of BLISSEY's egg be­ comes unfailingly caring and pleas­ ant to everyone.

name: raikou
flavor_text_entries: The rain clouds it carries let it fire thunderbolts at will. They say that it descended with lightning.

name: entei
flavor_text_entries: Volcanoes erupt when it barks. Un­ able to restrain its extreme power, it races headlong around the land.

name: suicune
flavor_text_entries: Said to be the reincarnation of north winds, it can instantly purify filthy, murky water.

name: larvitar
flavor_text_entries: It feeds on soil. After it has eaten a large mountain, it will fall asleep so it can grow.

name: pupitar
flavor_text_entries: Its shell is as hard as sheet rock, and it is also very strong. Its THRASHING can topple a mountain.

name: tyranitar
flavor_text_entries: Its body can't be harmed by any sort of attack, so it is very eager to make challenges against enemies.

name: lugia
flavor_text_entries: It is said that it quietly spends its time deep at the bottom of the sea because its powers are too strong.

name: ho-oh
flavor_text_entries: Legends claim this POKéMON flies the world's skies con­ tinuously on its magnificent seven- colored wings.

name: celebi
flavor_text_entries: This POKéMON wan­ ders across time. Grass and trees flourish in the forests in which it has appeared.

name: treecko
flavor_text_entries: TREECKO has small hooks on the bottom of its feet that enable it to scale vertical walls. This POKéMON attacks by slamming foes with its thick tail.

name: grovyle
flavor_text_entries: 발달한 넓적다리의 근육이 경이로운 순발력과 도약력을 만들어 낸다.

name: sceptile
flavor_text_entries: The leaves growing on SCEPTILE’s body are very sharp edged. This POKéMON is very agile - it leaps all over the branches of trees and jumps on its foe from above or behind.

name: torchic
flavor_text_entries: TORCHIC sticks with its TRAINER, following behind with unsteady steps. This POKéMON breathes fire of over 1,800 degrees F, including fireballs that leave the foe scorched black.

name: combusken
flavor_text_entries: COMBUSKEN toughens up its legs and thighs by running through fields and mountains. This POKéMON’s legs possess both speed and power, enabling it to dole out ten kicks in one second.

name: blaziken
flavor_text_entries: In battle, BLAZIKEN blows out intense flames from its wrists and attacks foes courageously. The stronger the foe, the more intensely this POKéMON’s wrists burn.

name: mudkip
flavor_text_entries: The fin on MUDKIP’s head acts as highly sensitive radar. Using this fin to sense movements of water and air, this POKéMON can determine what is taking place around it without using its eyes.

name: marshtomp
flavor_text_entries: The surface of MARSHTOMP’s body is enveloped by a thin, sticky film that enables it to live on land. This POKéMON plays in mud on beaches when the ocean tide is low.

name: swampert
flavor_text_entries: SWAMPERT is very strong. It has enough power to easily drag a boulder weighing more than a ton. This POKéMON also has powerful vision that lets it see even in murky water.

name: poochyena
flavor_text_entries: At first sight, POOCHYENA takes a bite at anything that moves. This POKéMON chases after prey until the victim becomes exhausted. However, it may turn tail if the prey strikes back.

name: mightyena
flavor_text_entries: Les Grahyèna forment des meutes de dix qui excellent au travail de groupe pour capturer leurs proies.

name: zigzagoon
flavor_text_entries: ZIGZAGOON restlessly wanders everywhere at all times. This POKéMON does so because it is very curious. It becomes interested in anything that it happens to see.

name: linoone
flavor_text_entries: LINOONE always runs full speed and only in straight lines. If facing an obstacle, it makes a right-angle turn to evade it. This POKéMON is very challenged by gently curving roads.

name: wurmple
flavor_text_entries: Using the spikes on its rear end,   WURMPLE peels the bark off trees and feeds on the sap that oozes out. This POKéMON’s feet are tipped with suction pads that allow it to cling to glass without slipping.

name: silcoon
flavor_text_entries: SILCOON tethers itself to a tree branch using silk to keep from falling. There,  this POKéMON hangs quietly while it awaits evolution. It peers out of the silk cocoon through a small hole.

name: beautifly
flavor_text_entries: BEAUTIFLY’s favorite food is the sweet pollen of flowers. If you want to see this POKéMON, just leave a potted flower by an open window. BEAUTIFLY is sure to come looking for pollen.

name: cascoon
flavor_text_entries: CASCOON makes its protective cocoon by wrapping its body entirely with a fine silk from its mouth. Once the silk goes around its body, it hardens. This POKéMON prepares for its evolution inside the cocoon.

name: dustox
flavor_text_entries: DUSTOX is instinctively drawn to light. Swarms of this POKéMON are attracted by the bright lights of cities, where they wreak havoc by stripping the leaves off roadside trees for food.

name: lotad
flavor_text_entries: LOTAD live in ponds and lakes, where they float on the surface. It grows weak if its broad leaf dies. On rare occasions, this POKéMON travels on land in search of clean water.

name: lombre
flavor_text_entries: Vive en el agua y, cuando hace sol, se queda en la orilla. De día duerme sobre las algas y de noche entra en acción.

name: ludicolo
flavor_text_entries: LUDICOLO begins dancing as soon as it hears cheerful, festive music. This POKéMON is said to appear when it hears the singing of children on hiking outings.

name: seedot
flavor_text_entries: SEEDOT attaches itself to a tree branch using the top of its head. It sucks moisture from the tree while hanging off the branch. The more water it drinks, the glossier this POKéMON’s body becomes.

name: nuzleaf
flavor_text_entries: NUZLEAF live in densely overgrown forests. They occasionally venture out of the forest to startle people. This POKéMON dislikes having its long nose pinched.

name: shiftry
flavor_text_entries: SHIFTRY is a mysterious POKéMON that is said to live atop towering trees  dating back over a thousand years. It creates terrific windstorms with the fans it holds.

name: taillow
flavor_text_entries: TAILLOW courageously stands its ground against foes, however strong they may be. This gutsy POKéMON will remain defiant even after a loss. On the other hand, it cries loudly if it becomes hungry.

name: swellow
flavor_text_entries: SWELLOW flies high above our heads, making graceful arcs in the sky. This POKéMON dives at a steep angle as soon as it spots its prey. The hapless prey is tightly grasped by SWELLOW’s clawed feet, preventing escape.

name: wingull
flavor_text_entries: 在海邊的懸崖上築巢。 會在海上盤旋，尋找牠 最愛吃的弱丁魚。

name: pelipper
flavor_text_entries: PELIPPER is a flying transporter that carries small POKéMON and eggs inside its massive bill. This POKéMON builds its nest on steep cliffs facing the sea.

name: ralts
flavor_text_entries: RALTS senses the emotions of people using the horns on its head. This POKéMON rarely appears before people. But when it does, it draws closer if it senses that the person has a positive disposition.

name: kirlia
flavor_text_entries: It is said that a KIRLIA that is exposed to the positive emotions of its TRAINER grows beautiful. This POKéMON controls psychokinetic powers with its highly developed brain.

name: gardevoir
flavor_text_entries: GARDEVOIR has the ability to read the future. If it senses impending danger to its TRAINER, this POKéMON is said to unleash its psychokinetic energy at full power.

name: surskit
flavor_text_entries: From the tips of its feet, SURSKIT secretes an oil that enables it to walk on water as if it were skating. This POKéMON feeds on microscopic organisms in ponds and lakes.

name: masquerain
flavor_text_entries: MASQUERAIN intimidates enemies with the eyelike patterns on its antennas. This POKéMON flaps its four wings to freely fly in any direction - even sideways and backwards - as if it were a helicopter.

name: shroomish
flavor_text_entries: SHROOMISH live in damp soil in the dark depths of forests. They are often found keeping still under fallen leaves. This POKéMON feeds on compost that is made up of fallen, rotted leaves.

name: breloom
flavor_text_entries: BRELOOM closes in on its foe with light and sprightly footwork, then throws punches with its stretchy arms. This POKéMON’s fighting technique puts boxers to shame.

name: slakoth
flavor_text_entries: SLAKOTH lolls around for over twenty hours every day. Because it moves so little, it does not need much food. This POKéMON’s sole daily meal consists of just three leaves.

name: vigoroth
flavor_text_entries: VIGOROTH is always itching and agitated to go on a wild rampage. It simply can’t tolerate sitting still for even a minute. This POKéMON’s stress level rises if it can’t be moving constantly.

name: slaking
flavor_text_entries: È il Pokémon più pigro del mondo, ma può sprigionare di colpo una quantità spaventosa di energia a lungo repressa.

name: nincada
flavor_text_entries: 有时能在土里生活１０年以上。 会从树木的根部那里吸取营养。

name: ninjask
flavor_text_entries: NINJASK moves around at such a high speed that it cannot be seen, even while its crying can be clearly heard. For that reason, this POKéMON was long believed to be invisible.

name: shedinja
flavor_text_entries: A discarded bug shell that came to life. Peering into the crack on its back is said to steal one’s spirit.

name: whismur
flavor_text_entries: Normally, WHISMUR’s voice is very quiet - it is barely audible even if one is paying close attention. However, if this POKéMON senses danger, it starts crying at an earsplitting volume.

name: loudred
flavor_text_entries: LOUDRED’s bellowing can completely decimate a wood-frame house. It uses its voice to punish its foes. This POKéMON’s round ears serve as loudspeakers.

name: exploud
flavor_text_entries: EXPLOUD triggers earthquakes with the tremors it creates by bellowing. If this POKéMON violently inhales from the ports on its body, it’s a sign that it is preparing to let loose a huge bellow.

name: makuhita
flavor_text_entries: MAKUHITA is tenacious - it will keep getting up and attacking its foe however many times it is knocked down. Every time it gets back up, this POKéMON stores more energy in its body for evolving.

name: hariyama
flavor_text_entries: HARIYAMA practices its straight-arm slaps in any number of locations. One hit of this POKéMON’s powerful, openhanded, straight-arm punches could snap a telephone pole in two.

name: azurill
flavor_text_entries: AZURILL spins its tail as if it were a lasso, then hurls it far. The momentum of the throw sends its body flying, too. Using this unique action, one of these POKéMON managed to hurl itself a record 33 feet.

name: nosepass
flavor_text_entries: NOSEPASS’s magnetic nose is always pointed to the north. If two of these POKéMON meet, they cannot turn their faces to each other when they are close because their magnetic noses repel one another.

name: skitty
flavor_text_entries: SKITTY has the habit of becoming fascinated by moving objects and chasing them around. This POKéMON is known to chase after its own tail and become dizzy.

name: delcatty
flavor_text_entries: DELCATTY prefers to live an unfettered existence in which it can do as it pleases at its own pace. Because this POKéMON eats and sleeps whenever it decides, its daily routines are completely random.

name: sableye
flavor_text_entries: SABLEYE lead quiet lives deep inside caverns. They are feared, however, because these POKéMON are thought to steal the spirits of people when their eyes burn with a sinister glow in the darkness.

name: mawile
flavor_text_entries: MAWHILE’s huge jaws are actually steel horns that have been transformed. Its docile-looking face serves to lull its foe into letting down its guard. When the foe least expects it, MAWHILE chomps it with its gaping jaws.

name: aron
flavor_text_entries: This POKéMON has a body of steel. To make its body, ARON feeds on iron ore that it digs from mountains. Occasionally, it causes major trouble by eating bridges and rails.

name: lairon
flavor_text_entries: Il raffole du minerai de fer. Il défend son territoire en chargeant avec son corps d’acier.

name: aggron
flavor_text_entries: AGGRON claims an entire mountain as its own territory. It mercilessly beats up anything that violates its environment. This POKéMON vigilantly patrols its territory at all times.

name: meditite
flavor_text_entries: MEDITITE undertakes rigorous mental training deep in the mountains. However, whenever it meditates, this POKéMON always loses its concentration and focus. As a result, its training never ends.

name: medicham
flavor_text_entries: It is said that through meditation, MEDICHAM heightens energy inside its body and sharpens its sixth sense. This POKéMON hides its presence by merging itself with fields and mountains.

name: electrike
flavor_text_entries: ELECTRIKE stores electricity in its long body hair. This POKéMON stimulates its leg muscles with electric charges. These jolts of power give its legs explosive acceleration performance.

name: manectric
flavor_text_entries: It rarely appears before people. It is said to nest where lightning has fallen.

name: plusle
flavor_text_entries: PLUSLE always acts as a cheerleader for its partners. Whenever a teammate puts out a good effort in battle, this POKéMON shorts out its body to create the crackling noises of sparks to show its joy.

name: minun
flavor_text_entries: MINUN is more concerned about cheering on its partners than its own safety. It shorts out the electricity in its body to create brilliant showers of sparks to cheer on its teammates.

name: volbeat
flavor_text_entries: With the arrival of night, VOLBEAT emits light from its tail. It communicates with others by adjusting the intensity and flashing of its light. This POKéMON is attracted by the sweet aroma of ILLUMISE.

name: illumise
flavor_text_entries: ILLUMISE attracts a swarm of VOLBEAT using a sweet fragrance. Once the VOLBEAT have gathered, this POKéMON leads the lit-up swarm in drawing geometric designs on the canvas of the night sky.

name: roselia
flavor_text_entries: 両手の　花を　ねらう　相手には 鋭い　トゲを　飛ばして　攻撃する。 花の　香りは　気持ちを　和ませる。

name: gulpin
flavor_text_entries: Virtually all of GULPIN’s body is its stomach. As a result, it can swallow something its own size. This POKéMON’s stomach contains a special fluid that digests anything.

name: swalot
flavor_text_entries: It swallows anything whole. It sweats toxic fluids from its follicles to douse foes.

name: carvanha
flavor_text_entries: CARVANHA’s strongly developed jaws and its sharply pointed fangs pack the destructive power to rip out boat hulls. Many boats have been attacked and sunk by this POKéMON.

name: sharpedo
flavor_text_entries: Nicknamed “the bully of the sea,” SHARPEDO is widely feared. Its cruel fangs grow back immediately if they snap off. Just one of these POKéMON can thoroughly tear apart a supertanker.

name: wailmer
flavor_text_entries: It bounces playfully like a ball. The more seawater it swallows, the higher it bounces.

name: wailord
flavor_text_entries: WAILORD is the largest of all identified POKéMON up to now. This giant POKéMON swims languorously in the vast open sea, eating massive amounts of food at once with its enormous mouth.

name: numel
flavor_text_entries: NUMEL is extremely dull witted - it doesn’t notice being hit. However, it can’t stand hunger for even a second. This POKéMON’s body is a seething cauldron of boiling magma.

name: camerupt
flavor_text_entries: CAMERUPT has a volcano inside its body. Magma of 18,000 degrees F courses through its body. Occasionally, the humps on this POKéMON’s back erupt, spewing the superheated magma.

name: torkoal
flavor_text_entries: TORKOAL digs through mountains in search of coal. If it finds some, it fills hollow spaces on its shell with the coal and burns it. If it is attacked, this POKéMON spouts thick black smoke to beat a retreat.

name: spoink
flavor_text_entries: SPOINK bounces around on its tail. The shock of its bouncing makes its heart pump. As a result, this POKéMON cannot afford to stop bouncing - if it stops, its heart will stop.

name: grumpig
flavor_text_entries: GRUMPIG uses the black pearls on its body to amplify its psychic power waves for gaining total control over its foe. When this POKéMON uses its special power, its snorting breath grows labored.

name: spinda
flavor_text_entries: All the SPINDA that exist in the world are said to have utterly unique spot patterns. The shaky, tottering steps of this POKéMON give it the appearance of dancing.

name: trapinch
flavor_text_entries: Its big jaws crunch through boulders. Because its head is so big, it has a hard time getting back upright if it tips over onto its back.

name: vibrava
flavor_text_entries: To make prey faint, VIBRAVA generates ultrasonic waves by vigorously making its two wings vibrate. This POKéMON’s ultrasonic waves are so powerful, they can bring on headaches in people.

name: flygon
flavor_text_entries: FLYGON is nicknamed “the elemental  spirit of the desert.” Because its flapping wings whip up a cloud of sand, this POKéMON is always enveloped in a sandstorm while flying.

name: cacnea
flavor_text_entries: CACNEA lives in arid locations such as deserts. It releases a strong aroma from its flower to attract prey. When prey comes near, this POKéMON shoots sharp thorns from its body to bring the victim down.

name: cacturne
flavor_text_entries: During the daytime, CACTURNE remains unmoving so that it does not lose any moisture to the harsh desert sun. This POKéMON becomes active at night when the temperature drops.

name: swablu
flavor_text_entries: SWABLU has light and fluffy wings that are like cottony clouds. This POKéMON is not frightened of people. It lands on the heads of people and sits there like a cotton-fluff hat.

name: altaria
flavor_text_entries: ALTARIA dances and wheels through the sky among billowing, cotton-like clouds. By singing melodies in its crystal-clear voice, this POKéMON makes its listeners experience dreamy wonderment.

name: zangoose
flavor_text_entries: Se sente anche solo l’odore di Seviper, gli si rizza la pelliccia. Lacera il nemico con artigli affilati.

name: seviper
flavor_text_entries: SEVIPER shares a generations-long feud with ZANGOOSE. The scars on its body are evidence of vicious battles. This POKéMON attacks using its sword- edged tail.

name: lunatone
flavor_text_entries: LUNATONE was discovered at a location where a meteorite fell. As a result, some people theorize that this POKéMON came from space. However, no one has been able to prove this theory so far.

name: solrock
flavor_text_entries: SOLROCK is a new species of POKéMON that is said to have fallen from space. It floats in air and moves silently. In battle, this POKéMON releases intensely bright light.

name: barboach
flavor_text_entries: BARBOACH’s sensitive whiskers serve as a superb radar system. This POKéMON hides in mud, leaving only its two whiskers exposed while it waits for prey to come along.

name: whiscash
flavor_text_entries: WHISCASH is extremely territorial. Just one of these POKéMON will claim a large pond as its exclusive territory. If a foe approaches it, it thrashes about and triggers a massive earthquake.

name: corphish
flavor_text_entries: CORPHISH were originally foreign POKéMON that were imported as pets. They eventually turned up in the wild. This POKéMON is very hardy and has greatly increased its population.

name: crawdaunt
flavor_text_entries: CRAWDAUNT has an extremely violent nature that compels it to challenge other living things to battle. Other life-forms refuse to live in ponds inhabited by this POKéMON, making them desolate places.

name: baltoy
flavor_text_entries: BALTOY moves while spinning around on its one foot. Primitive wall paintings depicting this POKéMON living among people were discovered in some ancient ruins.

name: claydol
flavor_text_entries: CLAYDOL are said to be dolls of mud made by primitive humans and brought to life by exposure to a mysterious ray. This POKéMON moves about while levitating.

name: lileep
flavor_text_entries: LILEEP became extinct approximately a hundred million years ago. This ancient POKéMON attaches itself to a rock on the seafloor and catches approaching prey using tentacles  shaped like flower petals.

name: cradily
flavor_text_entries: CRADILY roams around the ocean floor in search of food. This POKéMON freely extends its tree trunk-like neck and captures unwary prey using its eight tentacles.

name: anorith
flavor_text_entries: ANORITH was regenerated from a prehistoric fossil. This primitive POKéMON once lived in warm seas. It grips its prey firmly between its two large claws.

name: armaldo
flavor_text_entries: ARMALDO’s tough armor makes all attacks bounce off. This POKéMON’s two enormous claws can be freely extended or contracted. They have the power to punch right through a steel slab.

name: feebas
flavor_text_entries: FEEBAS’s fins are ragged and tattered from the start of its life. Because of its shoddy appearance, this POKéMON is largely ignored. It is capable of living in both the sea and in rivers.

name: milotic
flavor_text_entries: Es el Pokémon más hermoso del mundo. Milotic ha inspirado numerosas obras de arte.

name: castform
flavor_text_entries: CASTFORM’s appearance changes with the weather. This POKéMON gained the ability to use the vast power of nature to protect its tiny body.

name: kecleon
flavor_text_entries: KECLEON is capable of changing its body colors at will to blend in with its surroundings. There is one exception - this POKéMON can’t change the zigzag pattern on its belly.

name: shuppet
flavor_text_entries: SHUPPET is attracted by feelings of jealousy and vindictiveness. If someone develops strong feelings of vengeance, this POKéMON will appear in a swarm and line up beneath the eaves of that person’s home.

name: banette
flavor_text_entries: BANETTE generates energy for laying strong curses by sticking pins into its own body. This POKéMON was originally a pitiful plush doll that was thrown away.

name: duskull
flavor_text_entries: DUSKULL can pass through any wall no matter how thick it may be. Once this POKéMON chooses a target, it will doggedly pursue the intended victim until the break of dawn.

name: dusclops
flavor_text_entries: DUSCLOPS’s body is completely hollow - there is nothing at all inside. It is said that its body is like a black hole. This POKéMON will absorb anything into its body, but nothing will ever come back out.

name: tropius
flavor_text_entries: The bunches of fruit around TROPIUS’s neck are very popular with children. This POKéMON loves fruit, and eats it continuously. Apparently, its love for fruit resulted in its own outgrowth of fruit.

name: chimecho
flavor_text_entries: Emitting ultrasonic cries, it floats on winds to travel great distances.

name: absol
flavor_text_entries: Every time ABSOL appears before people, it is followed by a disaster such as an earthquake or a tidal wave. As a result, it came to be known as the disaster POKéMON.

name: wynaut
flavor_text_entries: WYNAUT can always be seen with a big, happy smile on its face. Look at its tail to determine if it is angry. When angered, this POKéMON will be slapping the ground with its tail.

name: snorunt
flavor_text_entries: SNORUNT live in regions with heavy snowfall. In seasons without snow, such as spring and summer, this POKéMON steals away to live quietly among stalactites and stalagmites deep in caverns.

name: glalie
flavor_text_entries: 從大大的嘴巴裡噴出寒氣， 把獵物瞬間凍得硬梆梆的， 然後大口咬碎享用。

name: spheal
flavor_text_entries: SPHEAL is much faster rolling than  walking to get around. When groups of this POKéMON eat, they all clap at once to show their pleasure. Because of this, their mealtimes are noisy.

name: sealeo
flavor_text_entries: SEALEO has the habit of always juggling on the tip of its nose anything it sees for the first time. This POKéMON occasionally entertains itself by balancing and rolling a SPHEAL on its nose.

name: walrein
flavor_text_entries: WALREIN’s two massively developed tusks can totally shatter blocks of ice weighing ten tons with one blow. This POKéMON’s thick coat of blubber insulates it from subzero temperatures.

name: clamperl
flavor_text_entries: CLAMPERL’s sturdy shell is not only good for protection - it is also used for clamping and catching prey. A fully grown CLAMPERL’s shell will be scored with nicks and scratches all over.

name: huntail
flavor_text_entries: It lives deep in the pitch-dark sea. It attracts prey by moving its tail in mimicry of a small animal.

name: gorebyss
flavor_text_entries: GOREBYSS lives in the southern seas at extreme depths. Its body is built to withstand the enormous pressure of water at incredible depths. Because of this, this POKéMON’s body is unharmed by ordinary attacks.

name: relicanth
flavor_text_entries: It has remained unchanged for 100 million years. It was discovered during a deep-sea exploration.

name: luvdisc
flavor_text_entries: LUVDISC live in shallow seas in the tropics. This heart-shaped POKéMON earned its name by swimming after loving couples it spotted in the ocean’s waves.

name: bagon
flavor_text_entries: BAGON has a dream of one day soaring in the sky. In doomed efforts to fly, this POKéMON hurls itself off cliffs. As a result of its dives, its head has  grown tough and as hard as tempered steel.

name: shelgon
flavor_text_entries: Inside SHELGON’s armor-like shell, cells are in the midst of transformation to create an entirely new body. This POKéMON’s shell is extremely heavy, making its movements sluggish.

name: salamence
flavor_text_entries: SALAMENCE came about as a result of a strong, long-held dream of growing wings. It is said that this powerful desire triggered a sudden mutation in this POKéMON’s cells, causing it to sprout its magnificent wings.

name: beldum
flavor_text_entries: Its cells are all magnetic, and it communicates with others by using magnetic pulses.

name: metang
flavor_text_entries: When two BELDUM fuse together, METANG is formed. The brains of the BELDUM are joined by a magnetic nervous system. By linking its brains magnetically, this POKéMON generates strong psychokinetic power.

name: metagross
flavor_text_entries: METAGROSS has four brains in total. Combined, the four brains can breeze through difficult calculations faster than a supercomputer. This POKéMON can float in the air by tucking in its four legs.

name: regirock
flavor_text_entries: REGIROCK was sealed away by people long ago. If this POKéMON’s body is damaged in battle, it is said to seek out suitable rocks on its own to repair itself.

name: regice
flavor_text_entries: REGICE’s body was made during an ice age. The deep-frozen body can’t be melted, even by fire. This POKéMON controls frigid air of minus 328 degrees F.

name: registeel
flavor_text_entries: REGISTEEL has a body that is harder than any kind of metal. Its body is apparently hollow. No one has any idea what this POKéMON eats.

name: latias
flavor_text_entries: LATIAS is highly sensitive to the emotions of people. If it senses any hostility, this POKéMON ruffles the feathers all over its body and cries shrilly to intimidate the foe.

name: latios
flavor_text_entries: Un Pokémon très intelligent. Il peut voler plus vite qu’un avion à réaction en repliant ses ailes.

name: kyogre
flavor_text_entries: KYOGRE has the power to create massive rain clouds that cover the entire sky and bring about torrential downpours. This POKéMON saved people who were suffering from droughts.

name: groudon
flavor_text_entries: GROUDON has long been described in  mythology as the POKéMON that raised lands and expanded continents. This POKéMON took to sleep after a cataclysmic battle with KYOGRE.

name: rayquaza
flavor_text_entries: RAYQUAZA lived for hundreds of millions of years in the earth’s ozone layer,  never descending to the ground. This POKéMON appears to feed on water and particles in the atmosphere.

name: jirachi
flavor_text_entries: A legend states that JIRACHI will make true any wish that is written on notes attached to its head when it awakens. If this POKéMON senses danger, it will fight without awakening.

name: turtwig
flavor_text_entries: Made from soil, the shell on its back hardens when it drinks water. It lives along lakes.

name: grotle
flavor_text_entries: 숲 속의 물가에서 산다. 낮에는 숲 밖으로 나와서 등껍질의 나무에 빛을 쬔다.

name: torterra
flavor_text_entries: Small Pokémon occasionally gather on its unmoving back to begin building their nests.

name: chimchar
flavor_text_entries: It agilely scales sheer cliffs to live atop craggy mountains. Its fire is put out when it sleeps.

name: monferno
flavor_text_entries: To intimidate attackers, it stretches the fire on its tail to make itself appear bigger.

name: infernape
flavor_text_entries: It uses a special kind of martial arts involving all its limbs. Its fire never goes out.

name: piplup
flavor_text_entries: Because it is very proud, it hates accepting food from people. Its thick down guards it from cold.

name: prinplup
flavor_text_entries: It lives alone, away from others. Apparently, every one of them believes it is the most important.

name: empoleon
flavor_text_entries: The three horns that extend from its beak attest to its power. The leader has the biggest horns.

name: starly
flavor_text_entries: They flock in great numbers. Though small, they flap their wings with great power.

name: staravia
flavor_text_entries: It flies around forests and fields in search of bug Pokémon. It stays within a huge flock.

name: staraptor
flavor_text_entries: It has a savage nature. It will courageously challenge foes that are much larger.

name: bidoof
flavor_text_entries: With nerves of steel, nothing can perturb it. It is more agile and active than it appears.

name: bibarel
flavor_text_entries: It makes its nest by damming streams with bark and mud. It is known as an industrious worker.

name: kricketot
flavor_text_entries: It shakes its head back to front, causing its antennae to hit each other and sound like a xylophone.

name: kricketune
flavor_text_entries: It crosses its knifelike arms in front of its chest when it cries. It can compose melodies ad lib.

name: shinx
flavor_text_entries: All of its fur dazzles if danger is sensed. It flees while the foe is momentarily blinded.

name: luxio
flavor_text_entries: Its claws loose electricity with enough amperage to cause fainting. They live in small groups.

name: luxray
flavor_text_entries: It has eyes that can see through anything. It spots and captures prey hiding behind objects.

name: budew
flavor_text_entries: Over the winter, it closes its bud and endures the cold. In spring, the bud opens and releases pollen.

name: roserade
flavor_text_entries: It attracts prey with a sweet aroma, then downs it with thorny whips hidden in its arms.

name: cranidos
flavor_text_entries: It lived in jungles around 100 million years ago. Its skull is as hard as iron.

name: rampardos
flavor_text_entries: Its powerful head butt has enough power to shatter even the most durable things upon impact.

name: shieldon
flavor_text_entries: A Pokémon that lived in jungles around 100 million years ago. Its facial hide is extremely hard.

name: bastiodon
flavor_text_entries: Any frontal attack is repulsed. It is a docile Pokémon that feeds on grass and berries.

name: burmy
flavor_text_entries: To shelter itself from cold, wintry winds, it covers itself with a cloak made of twigs and leaves.

name: mothim
flavor_text_entries: It loves the honey of flowers and steals honey collected by COMBEE.

name: combee
flavor_text_entries: A Pokémon formed by three others. It busily carries sweet floral honey to VESPIQUEN.

name: vespiquen
flavor_text_entries: Its abdomen is a honeycomb for grubs. It raises its grubs on honey collected by COMBEE.

name: pachirisu
flavor_text_entries: It makes fur balls that crackle with static electricity. It stores them with berries in tree holes.

name: buizel
flavor_text_entries: It has a flotation sac that is like an inflatable collar. It floats on water with its head out.

name: floatzel
flavor_text_entries: It floats using its well-developed flotation sac. It assists in the rescues of drowning people.

name: cherubi
flavor_text_entries: The small ball holds the nutrients needed for evolution. Apparently, it is very sweet and tasty.

name: cherrim
flavor_text_entries: It blooms during times of strong sunlight. It tries to make up for everything it endured as a bud.

name: shellos
flavor_text_entries: Cambia facilmente aspetto e colore secondo il luogo di provenienza.

name: gastrodon
flavor_text_entries: It has a pliable body without any bones. If any part of its body is torn off, it grows right back.

name: ambipom
flavor_text_entries: To eat, it deftly shucks nuts with its two tails. It rarely uses its arms now.

name: drifloon
flavor_text_entries: Pokémon formato dalle anime di persone e Pokémon. Ama le stagioni umide.

name: drifblim
flavor_text_entries: It’s drowzy in daytime, but flies off in the evening in big groups. No one knows where they go.

name: buneary
flavor_text_entries: It slams foes by sharply uncoiling its rolled ears. It stings enough to make a grown-up cry in pain.

name: lopunny
flavor_text_entries: An extremely cautious Pokémon. It cloaks its body with its fluffy ear fur when it senses danger.

name: mismagius
flavor_text_entries: Its cries sound like incantations. Those hearing it are tormented by headaches and hallucinations.

name: honchkrow
flavor_text_entries: Becoming active at night, it is known to swarm with numerous MURKROW in tow.

name: glameow
flavor_text_entries: It claws if displeased and purrs when affectionate. Its fickleness is very popular among some.

name: purugly
flavor_text_entries: Para intimidar y parecer más corpulento, se aprieta la cintura con su cola bífida.

name: chingling
flavor_text_entries: It emits cries by agitating an orb at the back of its throat. It moves with flouncing hops.

name: stunky
flavor_text_entries: It protects itself by spraying a noxious fluid from its rear. The stench lingers for 24 hours.

name: skuntank
flavor_text_entries: It sprays a vile-smelling fluid from the tip of its tail to attack. Its range is over 160 feet.

name: bronzor
flavor_text_entries: Implements shaped like it were discovered in ancient tombs. It is unknown if they are related.

name: bronzong
flavor_text_entries: One caused a news sensation when it was dug up at a construction site after a 2,000-year sleep.

name: bonsly
flavor_text_entries: It prefers an arid atmosphere. It leaks water that looks like tears when adjusting its moisture level.

name: mime-jr
flavor_text_entries: It habitually mimics foes. Once mimicked, the foe cannot take its eyes off this Pokémon.

name: happiny
flavor_text_entries: It loves round white things. It carries an egg-shaped rock in imitation of CHANSEY.

name: chatot
flavor_text_entries: It can learn and speak human words. If they gather, they all learn the same saying.

name: spiritomb
flavor_text_entries: A Pokémon that was formed by 108 spirits. It is bound to a fissure in an odd keystone.

name: gible
flavor_text_entries: It nests in small, horizontal holes in cave walls. It pounces to catch prey that stray too close.

name: gabite
flavor_text_entries: There is a long-held belief that medicine made from its scales will heal even incurable illnesses.

name: garchomp
flavor_text_entries: Quando si piega e distende le ali, sembra un jet. Vola a una velocità supersonica.

name: munchlax
flavor_text_entries: It wolfs down its weight in food once a day, swallowing food whole with almost no chewing.

name: riolu
flavor_text_entries: The aura that emanates from its body intensifies to alert others if it is afraid or sad.

name: lucario
flavor_text_entries: It has the ability to sense the auras of all things. It understands human speech.

name: hippopotas
flavor_text_entries: It lives in arid places. Instead of perspiration, it expels grainy sand from its body.

name: hippowdon
flavor_text_entries: It blasts internally stored sand from ports on its body to create a towering twister for attack.

name: skorupi
flavor_text_entries: It grips prey with its tail claws and injects poison. It tenaciously hangs on until the poison takes.

name: drapion
flavor_text_entries: It has the power in its clawed arms to make scrap of a car. The tips of its claws release poison.

name: croagunk
flavor_text_entries: Its cheeks hold poison sacs. It tries to catch foes off guard to jab them with toxic fingers.

name: toxicroak
flavor_text_entries: Its knuckle claws secrete a toxin so vile that even a scratch could prove fatal.

name: carnivine
flavor_text_entries: It attracts prey with its sweet- smelling saliva, then chomps down. It takes a whole day to eat prey.

name: finneon
flavor_text_entries: After long exposure to sunlight, the patterns on its tail fins shine vividly when darkness arrives.

name: lumineon
flavor_text_entries: It lives on the deep-sea floor. It attracts prey by flashing the patterns on its four tail fins.

name: mantyke
flavor_text_entries: A friendly Pokémon that captures the subtle flows of seawater using its two antennae.

name: snover
flavor_text_entries: It lives on snowy mountains. Having had little contact with humans, it is boldly inquisitive.

name: abomasnow
flavor_text_entries: It whips up blizzards in mountains that are always buried in snow. It is the abominable snowman.

name: weavile
flavor_text_entries: They live in cold regions, forming groups of four or five that hunt prey with impressive coordination.

name: magnezone
flavor_text_entries: It evolved from exposure to a special magnetic field. Three units generate magnetism.

name: lickilicky
flavor_text_entries: It wraps things with its extensible tongue. Getting too close to it will leave you soaked with drool.

name: rhyperior
flavor_text_entries: It puts rocks in holes in its palms and uses its muscles to shoot them. GEODUDE are shot at rare times.

name: tangrowth
flavor_text_entries: It ensnares prey by extending arms made of vines. Losing arms to predators does not trouble it.

name: electivire
flavor_text_entries: It pushes the tips of its two tails against the foe, then lets loose with over 20,000 volts of power.

name: magmortar
flavor_text_entries: It blasts fireballs of over 3,600 degrees F from the ends of its arms. It lives in volcanic craters.

name: togekiss
flavor_text_entries: It will never appear where there is strife. Its sightings have become rare recently.

name: yanmega
flavor_text_entries: Seine bevorzugte Strategie besteht darin, seine Gegner aus dem Flug blitzartig zur Strecke zu bringen.

name: leafeon
flavor_text_entries: Just like a plant, it uses photosynthesis. As a result, it is always enveloped in clear air.

name: glaceon
flavor_text_entries: As a protective technique, it can completely freeze its fur to make its hairs stand like needles.

name: gliscor
flavor_text_entries: It observes prey while hanging inverted from branches. When the chance presents itself, it swoops!

name: mamoswine
flavor_text_entries: Its impressive tusks are made of ice. The population thinned when it turned warm after the ice age.

name: porygon-z
flavor_text_entries: Additional software was installed to make it a better Pokémon. It began acting oddly, however.

name: gallade
flavor_text_entries: A master of courtesy and swordsmanship, it fights using extending swords on its elbows.

name: probopass
flavor_text_entries: Il utilise sa force magnétique pour diriger trois petites unités appelées Mini-nez.

name: dusknoir
flavor_text_entries: Man sagt, dass es verlorene Seelen in seinem biegsamen Körper nach Hause geleite.

name: froslass
flavor_text_entries: It freezes foes with an icy breath nearly -60 degrees F. What seems to be its body is actually hollow.

name: rotom
flavor_text_entries: Un Pokémon longtemps étudié comme source d’énergie pour un moteur très spécial.

name: uxie
flavor_text_entries: Known as “The Being of Knowledge.” It is said that it can wipe out the memory of those who see its eyes.

name: mesprit
flavor_text_entries: Known as “The Being of Emotion.” It taught humans the nobility of sorrow, pain, and joy.

name: azelf
flavor_text_entries: It is thought that Uxie, Mesprit, and Azelf all came from the same egg.

name: dialga
flavor_text_entries: It has the power to control time. It appears in Sinnoh-region myths as an ancient deity.

name: palkia
flavor_text_entries: It has the ability to distort space. It is described as a deity in Sinnoh-region mythology.

name: heatran
flavor_text_entries: It dwells in volcanic caves. It digs in with its cross-shaped feet to crawl on ceilings and walls.

name: regigigas
flavor_text_entries: There is an enduring legend that states this Pokémon towed continents with ropes.

name: cresselia
flavor_text_entries: Shiny particles are released from its wings like a veil. It is said to represent the crescent moon.

name: phione
flavor_text_entries: A Pokémon that lives in warm seas. It inflates the flotation sac on its head to drift and search for food.

name: manaphy
flavor_text_entries: Born on a cold seafloor, it will swim great distances to return to its birthplace.

name: darkrai
flavor_text_entries: It can lull people to sleep and make them dream. It is active during nights of the new moon.

name: arceus
flavor_text_entries: It is told in mythology that this Pokémon was born before the universe even existed.

name: victini
flavor_text_entries: Un Pokémon qui amène la victoire. On dit que les Dresseurs qui le possèdent peuvent gagner n’importe quel combat.

name: snivy
flavor_text_entries: Un Pokémon intelligent et très calme. Lorsqu’il a reçu suffisamment de lumière du soleil, il devient plus agile.

name: servine
flavor_text_entries: Il court comme s’il glissait sur le sol. Il déroute l’ennemi par ses mouvements et l’assomme d’un coup de liane.

name: serperior
flavor_text_entries: Il peut paralyser l’ennemi d’un regard. Il amplifie l’énergie du soleil dans son corps.

name: tepig
flavor_text_entries: Il évite agilement les attaques ennemies et crache des boules de feu par le groin. Il aime griller des Baies pour les manger.

name: pignite
flavor_text_entries: Quand le feu dans son corps s’embrase, sa vitesse et son agilité augmentent. En cas d’urgence, il crache de la fumée.

name: emboar
flavor_text_entries: Il embrase ses poings avec les flammes sur son menton et cogne l’ennemi avec. C’est un Pokémon très solidaire.

name: oshawott
flavor_text_entries: Il combat avec le coupillage de son ventre. Il peut parer un assaut et immédiatement contre-attaquer.

name: dewott
flavor_text_entries: L’apprentissage de sa technique de combat, qui utilise élégamment ses deux coupillages, est extrêmement rigoureux.

name: samurott
flavor_text_entries: Il peut terrasser ses ennemis d’un coup de la lame enchâssée dans son armure, et les faire taire d’un seul regard.

name: patrat
flavor_text_entries: Ils stockent à manger dans leurs bajoues et font le guet indéfiniment. Ils se font des signes en remuant la queue.

name: watchog
flavor_text_entries: Il attaque en crachant les graines des Baies qu’il accumule dans ses bajoues. S’il voit un ennemi, il dresse la queue.

name: lillipup
flavor_text_entries: Il fait vaillamment face à des ennemis très puissants, mais il est intelligent et évite les combats trop inégaux.

name: herdier
flavor_text_entries: Les poils qui entourent son corps comme un manteau sont extrêmement durs et amortissent les coups.

name: stoutland
flavor_text_entries: Il sauve les gens bloqués dans les montagnes par des tempêtes de neige. Ses longs poils le protègent du froid.

name: purrloin
flavor_text_entries: Il vole les gens pour le plaisir, mais il est tellement mignon que ses victimes finissent toujours par lui pardonner.

name: liepard
flavor_text_entries: Un Pokémon insaisissable. Son style et son pelage magnifique attirent de nombreux Dresseurs.

name: pansage
flavor_text_entries: Il vit dans les forêts profondes. Manger la feuille qui pousse sur sa tête fait disparaître la fatigue.

name: simisage
flavor_text_entries: Il a un tempérament violent et se bat avec sa queue pleine d’épines. La feuille sur sa tête est très amère.

name: pansear
flavor_text_entries: Quand il s’énerve, la mèche sur sa tête chauffe à 300 °C. Il s’en sert pour griller des Baies et les manger.

name: simisear
flavor_text_entries: Il adore les aliments sucrés. Ils lui servent d’énergie pour alimenter le feu à l’intérieur de son corps.

name: panpour
flavor_text_entries: L’eau contenue dans la mèche sur sa tête est pleine de nutriments. Elle fait pousser les plantes avec vigueur.

name: simipour
flavor_text_entries: Il stocke de l’eau dans les mèches de sa tête. Quand il est à sec, il se ravitaille en aspirant de l’eau par la queue.

name: munna
flavor_text_entries: Quand Munna mange un rêve, celui-ci est aussitôt oublié par le rêveur. Il lévite en permanence.

name: musharna
flavor_text_entries: La fumée qui sort de son front contient les rêves de nombreuses personnes et ceux de nombreux Pokémon.

name: pidove
flavor_text_entries: Il suit scrupuleusement les consignes de son Dresseur, mais il a du mal à comprendre les ordres trop compliqués.

name: tranquill
flavor_text_entries: Aussi éloigné qu’il puisse se trouver, il parvient toujours à retourner auprès de son Dresseur.

name: unfezant
flavor_text_entries: Le mâle intimide ses ennemis avec ses caroncules. La femelle vole mieux que le mâle.

name: blitzle
flavor_text_entries: Leur crinière scintille quand ils lâchent une décharge électrique. Ils se servent de ces scintillements pour communiquer.

name: zebstrika
flavor_text_entries: Il réagit à la vitesse de l’éclair. Lorsqu’il est en plein galop, on peut entendre le grondement du tonnerre.

name: roggenrola
flavor_text_entries: Il a une oreille hexagonale. Son corps, compressé dans des strates profondes, est dur comme de l’acier.

name: boldore
flavor_text_entries: Quand il est gonflé à bloc, ses cristaux orangés scintillent. Il cherche de l’eau souterraine dans les grottes.

name: gigalith
flavor_text_entries: Il comprime de l’énergie dans son corps, et ses attaques sont assez puissantes pour renverser des montagnes.

name: woobat
flavor_text_entries: Il vit dans les forêts sombres et les grottes. Il émet des ultrasons par le nez pour se diriger.

name: swoobat
flavor_text_entries: Il émet des ondes sonores de différentes fréquences par le nez. Certaines peuvent briser des rochers.

name: drilbur
flavor_text_entries: Il peut creuser à plus de 50 km/h et faire la course avec une voiture roulant sur le terrain qu’il creuse.

name: excadrill
flavor_text_entries: Ses vrilles en acier peuvent transpercer des poutres en fer. Il est très employé dans la construction de tunnels.

name: audino
flavor_text_entries: Il ausculte les gens avec ses antennes auriculaires pour juger de leurs émotions ou de leur santé.

name: timburr
flavor_text_entries: Il combat avec une poutre. Quand il en arrive à transporter de lourds madriers sans problème, l’évolution est proche.

name: gurdurr
flavor_text_entries: Même une armée de catcheurs se jetant sur son corps hyper musclé ne le ferait pas ciller.

name: conkeldurr
flavor_text_entries: Es setzt Attacken ein, die sich die Zentrifugalkraft zunutze machen, indem es seine Betonpfeiler umherschwingt.

name: tympole
flavor_text_entries: Il prévient ses camarades du danger en faisant vibrer ses joues pour générer un signal d’alarme très aigu.

name: palpitoad
flavor_text_entries: Quand il fait vibrer la bosse sur sa tête, il provoque des ondulations dans l’eau, mais aussi des tremblements de terre.

name: seismitoad
flavor_text_entries: Il fait gicler un liquide paralysant des pustules sur sa tête, et attaque ses ennemis à coups de vibrations.

name: throh
flavor_text_entries: Quand il noue sa ceinture, il devient plus puissant. Les Judokrak sauvages tressent leur ceinture avec des lianes.

name: sawk
flavor_text_entries: Dans les montagnes où il s’entraîne, on peut l’entendre donner des coups de poing aux rochers et aux grands arbres.

name: sewaddle
flavor_text_entries: Quand il éclot, Manternel lui coud son vêtement. Il dort en cachant son visage sous sa capuche.

name: swadloon
flavor_text_entries: Dans les forêts où il vit, la végétation pousse bien car il transforme les feuilles mortes en engrais.

name: leavanny
